race.comment: MIGHTY SCAR (8) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (24.59) at Sale in a T3 Grade 7. Lines up from box 8 for the first time. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Winning claims. SUNNY LYN (1) hit the frame last time at this track but just a few starts ago ran slick time when scoring over 510m at Sale in 28.82. Must include on winning run three back. EYEWITNESS (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (25.28) in a T3 Grade 7 at Sale. Shapes as one to consider. RALPH WIGGUM (6) placed last time and is worth some thought.
